    <summary>VeraCrypt is a free disk encryption software that is based on TrueCrypt 7.1a.</summary>
    <description>
VeraCrypt adds enhanced security to the algorithms used for system and partitions
encryption making it immune to new developments in brute-force attacks.
VeraCrypt also solves many vulnerabilities and security issues found in TrueCrypt.
The following post describes some of the enhancements and corrections done:
[https://veracrypt.codeplex.com/discussions/569777#PostContent_1313325]()

### Uninstallation

This package contains *no* uninstallation script!

Uninstallation can be achieved by using the
[automatic Uninstaller](https://github.com/chocolatey/choco/wiki/CommandsUninstall)-Feature
of chocolately.
To activate this feature please run the following command:

    choco feature enable -n autoUninstaller

### Security

This package verifies the downloaded installer via SHA1 checksum.
</description>
